    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187960/extras/60fc6774a6f70edfff16c0fc58867dfe.poster.avif?t=1764757629\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187960/extras/60fc6774a6f70edfff16c0fc58867dfe.webm?t=1764757629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187960/extras/60fc6774a6f70edfff16c0fc58867dfe.mp4?t=1764757629\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对大型多人游戏的新演绎。我们汲取 MMORPG 的精华，为重视时间与爽快玩法的现代玩家重新打造。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187960/extras/df445d9a237244e15811b1e093a79da6.poster.avif?t=1764757629\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187960/extras/df445d9a237244e15811b1e093a79da6.webm?t=1764757629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187960/extras/df445d9a237244e15811b1e093a79da6.mp4?t=1764757629\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进行制造与交易、持续致富，强化基地、角色与武器库——成为服务器上最成功的玩家！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187960/extras/c0c2dd5cfa8d1cbf9d0eb682b861bba9.poster.avif?t=1764757629\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187960/extras/c0c2dd5cfa8d1cbf9d0eb682b861bba9.webm?t=1764757629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187960/extras/c0c2dd5cfa8d1cbf9d0eb682b861bba9.mp4?t=1764757629\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 前往硬核 PvE 任务获取稀有材料，或组建默契十足的 PvP 小队，横扫各类锦标赛的奖励。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187960/extras/4e765c7d192979b35527092851cfa8fd.poster.avif?t=1764757629\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187960/extras/4e765c7d192979b35527092851cfa8fd.webm?t=1764757629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187960/extras/4e765c7d192979b35527092851cfa8fd.mp4?t=1764757629\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >投入大规模公会战争，占领领土，从游戏内贸易中分成，成为整个服务器的噩梦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187960/extras/25e481156e706c68d3279e7bdf05408c.poster.avif?t=1764757629\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187960/extras/25e481156e706c68d3279e7bdf05408c.webm?t=1764757629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187960/extras/25e481156e706c68d3279e7bdf05408c.mp4?t=1764757629\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >METACRAFT: Arena 提供广泛的 PvP 与 PvE 活动，可灵活适配你的游玩风格。向所有人证明，真正的冠军就是你！</p>",
